   273	
   274	**Streamlined Campaign Workflow:**
   275	1. Marketing PM identifies campaign need (quarterly market rates, sector content, etc.)
   276	2. Selects saved search: "All brokers in healthcare sector, SF territory, opted in"
   277	3. Customizes email content (can use templates for faster creation)
