   395	
   396	### Your Business Requirements
   397	
   398	**REQ-M015: Marketing early visibility into RFP opportunities (ACCOMMODATE)**
   399	- Current pain: "Marketing has no visibility until formal request submitted" via Asana
   400	- Impact: "Can't proactively prepare"; missed opportunity to prepare materials/resources
   401	- Future need: Marketing team sees pipeline early, identifies upcoming RFPs, resources appropriately
