   418	
   419	### Current State Process
   420	
   421	**RFP Identification & Request:**
   422	1. Relationship-based RFP identified by BD rep
   423	2. Preliminary assessment by rep
   424	3. When formal RFP arrives → Created as opportunity (sometimes)
   425	4. **Formal Asana request submitted by BD rep**
