   530	Lead capture occurs through multiple channels feeding into HubSpot:
   531	
   532	- Website forms \(contact forms, project inquiry, Sandbox booking\)
   533	- Internal visitor forms for showroom events
   534	- Trade shows and A&D events \(manual data capture\)
