   910	## Implementation Considerations & Risks
   911	
   912	### High Priority - Critical Success Factors
   913	
   914	1. **Contact Role & Sector Taxonomy Definition**
   915	   - Timing: Weeks 1-2 (blocking configuration)
   916	   - Participants: Marketing team, Sales GMs, Business Development
