   921	   - Timing: Weeks 3-6 (blocking go-live)
   922	   - Activity: Historical contact classification and cleanup
   923	   - Effort: Significant manual work depending on contact volume
   924	   - Risk: Incomplete classification → "poo in, poo out" continues
   925	
   926	3. **RFP Workflow Design**
   927	   - Timing: Weeks 2-3 (blocking configuration)
   928	   - Participants: Marketing, Sales, Business Development
   929	   - Deliverable: RFP request form specification, workflow routing rules
   930	   - Risk: Misaligned workflow → team resistance, Asana not retired
   931	
   932	### Medium Priority - Important Considerations
   933	
   934	4. **Change Management & User Adoption**
   935	   - Sales team required field discipline: Training and change management needed
   936	   - Admin team lead qualification: Clear guidelines and decision framework
   937	   - Marketing team capability building: New tools, new dashboards, new process
   938	
   939	5. **Parallel Asana/NetSuite Process**
   940	   - Recommendation: Run both systems 2-4 weeks
   941	   - Ensures smooth transition; catches workflow gaps
   942	   - Allows teams to validate new process before Asana retirement
   943	
   944	6. **Market Intelligence Dashboard Requirements**
   945	   - Timing: Weeks 3-4 (blocking configuration)
   946	   - Participants: Marketing team with analyst/BI support
   947	   - Deliverable: Dashboard design, metric definitions, access controls
   948	   - Risk: Unclear requirements → dashboard doesn't drive strategic decisions
