   693	
   694	NetSuite Orion provides comprehensive marketing analytics with sophisticated attribution capabilities specifically designed for complex B2B scenarios\. To accommodate Pivot's unique influencer marketing model, we will modify the order team assignment utilities to enable sophisticated attribution reporting\. This custom approach allows assigning influence percentages to different contributors on opportunities, providing granular visibility into how various influencer relationships drive revenue\.
