    15	| Merged-company COO | **Matt Denning** | KBM Hogue's COO; ultimate decision-maker |
    16	| Pivot leadership | **Sandra Rudloff** | |
    17	| GSI leadership | **Dustin Doucette**, **Jennifer Trask** | Both surnames are different — do not assume "Trask" applies to both |
